Victoria Bush https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victoria_Bush 0 Victoria Bush (born 15 January 1978) is a British actress and comedian, mostly known for her role as school secretary "Sonya Donnegan " in BBC 1's drama series Waterloo Road. She is also known for her role as Tina Purvis, Julie O'Kane and later known as Tina O'Kane, on the British television drama Bad Girls.
